59. A MGC shall invest only in the following instruments:
(1) Government Securities;
(2) Securities of corporate bodies/ public sector undertakings guaranteed by
Government;
(3) Fixed Deposit/ Certificate of Deposits/ bonds of Scheduled Commercial
banks/ PFIs;
(4) listed and rated debentures/ bonds of corporates;
(5) fully debt oriented Mutual Fund Units; and
(6) unquoted Government securities and Government guaranteed bonds.
